dct_description_sm: From British surveys between 1854 and 1882 with additions from United States and Fiji Govt. surveys.
Depths shown by soundings; relief by hachures and spot heights.
Shows depths, islands, shoals, reefs, drainage, peaks.
[Inset] : Fiji Islands : Continuation of group to southward (See Chart No. 409).
